# DeadPad Text Editor

Install:
```
pip install deadpad
```

Run:

```
deadpad <filename>
```

> A command line text editor made without curses or any other TUI library.

![](https://github.com/FrewtyPebbles/DeadPad-CLI-Text-Editor/blob/main/preview/deadpad2.gif)
